test_metrics = {}
for train_year in tqdm(sorted(years)):
    print(train_year)
    print('---*---'*4)
    year_df = df[df.year == int(train_year)].copy()
    dls = year_data.dataloaders(year_df, bs=4, num_workers=0)
    for epoch in range(3):
        learn = cnn_learner(dls,resnet18,metrics=accuracy, cbs=[SaveModelCallback(monitor='f1_score')])
        with learn.no_bar():
            learn.fine_tune(10)
        #metrics = learner.recorder.values
        test_df = df[df['year'] != train_year].copy()
        preds = learn.get_preds(dl=learn.dls.test_dl(test_df), with_decoded=True)
        pred_str =['text_only' if y == 0 else 'visual' for y in preds[2].tolist()]
        test_df['correct']  = test_df['label'] == pred_str
        test_df['correct'].replace({True:1, False: 0},inplace=True)  
        test_dict = test_df.groupby(['year'])['correct'].agg('mean').to_dict()
        
        test_metrics[f'{train_year}_epoch'] = test_dict
